<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1575] HMaster does not handle ZK session expiration</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1575</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the master does nothing when he gets a KeeperState.Expired event from ZK. That means that a new master will be elected but the other will still be there doing weird stuff.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12428701">HBASE-1575</key>
            <summary>HMaster does not handle ZK session expiration</summary>
